snippet.title: Battle Bolts Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
Battle Bolts on Steam: http://bit.ly/battlebolts-st
Early playable alpha available on Itch.io: http://bit.ly/battlebolts-itch

Battle Bolts is a strategy multiplayer game where up to 4 players battle in a deadly arena by programming their moves in advance!

For all things Battle Bolts check out the official social media channels:
🐦 http://twitter.com/BattleBolts
👍 http://facebook.com/battlebolts

Follow Croteam on Twitter and Instagram, like us on Facebook and don’t forget to join our ever-growing Croteam family on Discord and Reddit:

💬 http://discord.gg/croteam
🤩 http://reddit.com/r/croteam
🐦 http://twitter.com/croteam
👍 http://facebook.com/croteam
📸 http://instagram.com/officialcroteam
